    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor for the first time! I\u2019ve pampered this car since day one, keeping it garage-stored and spotless. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for its next big adventure, you\u2019ve found it. Drop me a message and let's get you behind the wheel! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
